      <title>市场消化特朗普和中国影响 油价有望本周上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价下跌，但仍有望实现周线上涨，因为市场正在消化特朗普第二任总统的影响，包括是否会刺激第一大进口国中国扩大刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
